{
  "id": "adv_main_02_11_04",
  "title": "東京編2章29話",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk001.m4a",
      "text": "さっきは随分、ご立派に啖呵切ったわね\nそこまで悪意を向けられるようなこと、したかしら？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were quite grandstanding back there.\nHave I done anything to deserve that much malice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依さん達から聞きました\nあなた達の目的も、そして、やり方も",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I heard from Rui-san and the others.\nYour purpose‚ and your methods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 14.2666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃんの残したものを全部奪って、消し去るって\n……そのためなら手段は選ばないんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're going to take everything my sister left behind and erase it‚\n…and you won't hesitate to use any means to achieve that?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 22.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk002.m4a",
      "text": "聞き捨てならないわね\n私達三人は、恥じるようなことは何もしてないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I can't just ignore that.\nWe three haven't done anything to be ashamed of.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 29.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk003.m4a",
      "text": "ステージの上で、正々堂々、実力で勝負している",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We compete fairly and squarely‚ with our skills‚ on stage.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 29.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 34.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "でも、姫野さんのやり口は知っているんですよね？\nその上で、見ないようにしている。違いますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But you know Himeno-san's methods‚ don't you?\nYou're choosing to turn a blind eye to it. Am I wrong?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 43.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk004.m4a",
      "text": "あの人が何をしようと、あの人の勝手だもの\n私達がやるべきことは変わらないわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Whatever she does is her business.\nWhat we have to do doesn't change.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.7,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 50.6
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk005.m4a",
      "text": "……そうやって固執するのは、負けた時に\n姫野さんの暗躍のせいだって言い訳したいから？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Are you being so stubborn because you want to make excuses\nand blame Himeno-san's schemes when you lose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 57.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "違います。それに、負けませんよ、私達は\nあなた達にも、姫野さんの陰謀にも",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's not true. And besides‚ we won't lose.\nNot to you‚ and not to Himeno-san's conspiracies.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 64.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 68.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "純粋に実力だけで、全部覆してみせますから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We'll overturn everything purely with our skills.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.3,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 72.5333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_designcorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "designcorridor-00",
      "startTime": 77.9333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk006.m4a",
      "text": "そう……なら楽しみにしているわ、妹さん\nそれじゃあ、さようなら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I see… Then I'm looking forward to it‚ little sister.\nWell then‚ goodbye.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 77.9333333333,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9500,
          "startTime": 82.0333333333
        },
