    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 84.7666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_rival-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 85.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "お帰り～。なんか麻奈の妹めっちゃ気合い入ってたね～\nもしかしてトリエルから話聞いてるのかな？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Welcome back～。 Mana's little sister was super fired up‚ wasn't she?\nMaybe she heard about it from TRINITYAiLE?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "恐らくね。あの様子だと、トリエルの三人は今",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Probably. From the looks of it‚ the three from TRINITYAiLE are currently",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 96.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "星見プロで厄介になっているんでしょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "causing trouble at Hoshimi Pro.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 104.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mhk",
      "speakerName": "miho",
      "speakerNameEn": "miho",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-miho.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-mhk008.m4a",
      "text": "……もういいですよ、その話は\n蒸し返されると、なおさら疲れてきます……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…That's enough about that.\nDredging it up again just makes me even more tired…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 107.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 110.1333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "あらら、武田さんご立腹～？\nあはは、ウケる～。格下相手にムキになっちゃってさ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh my‚ is Takeda-san angry～?\nAhaha‚ that's hilarious～。 Getting worked up over someone inferior.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.5666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "そういうあなたも、イラついてるんじゃないの？\nペラペラ喋って、バカみたい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're the one who's irritated‚ aren't you?\nChattering away like an idiot.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 122.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 124.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　何余裕ぶっこいてんの？\nあんたもせいぜい足引っ張んないよう練習しといてね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? Who do you think you are‚ acting all high and mighty?\nYou better practice so you don't drag us down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 129.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 132.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "誰に向かって言ってるの？\n足引っ張るとしたらあなたでしょ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Who are you talking to?\nYou're the one who's going to drag us down.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 137.8333333333
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "チッ、なになにリーダー気取り？\n調子に乗らないで下さいます～？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Tch‚ what‚ acting like a leader?\nDon't get cocky‚ will ya～?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 142.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dressingroom-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dressingroom-00",
      "startTime": 145.4666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "その辺にしておきなさい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's enough.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.4666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "姫野霧子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kiriko",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "誰かに聞かれでもしたらどうするつもり？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What are you going to do if someone overhears you?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 147.6,
      "sfxList": []
    },
