      "text": "あれからしばらく経った今だからこそ\n私、自分なりの答えが見つかりそうなんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that some time has passed since then‚\nI think I'm close to finding my own answer.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 326.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn019.m4a",
      "text": "私にとってのアイドル活動には\nもう、お姉ちゃんはあまり関係なくなっている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "To me‚ my sister doesn't have much to do\nwith my idol activities anymore.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 332.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn020.m4a",
      "text": "もちろんそれは、お姉ちゃんを忘れたとか\nそういうんじゃなくて……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Of course‚ that doesn't mean I've forgotten my sister‚\nor anything like that…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 339.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn021.m4a",
      "text": "あの日、お姉ちゃんと約束したんです\nお姉ちゃんじゃなく、ちゃんとファンと向き合おうって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made a promise with my sister that day.\nThat I would properly face the fans‚ not as her.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 345.4,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn022.m4a",
      "text": "沢山の人に楽しんでもらうアイドルを目指すって\nその思いで、今日まで歩み続けてきた。だから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd aim to be an idol who brings joy to many people.\nI've been moving forward with that feeling until today. So…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 354.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "……だからスリクスにも、堂々と立ち向かえたんだな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…So that's why you were able to boldly face ⅢX.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 359.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 364.0666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn023.m4a",
      "text": "はい……あの人達は、未だにお姉ちゃんを見ている\n自分達の目的を、重視し過ぎている",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes… Those people are still looking at my sister.\nThey're too focused on their own goals.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 369.9333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/mainStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04/sud_vo_adv_main_02_11_04-ktn024.m4a",
      "text": "アイドルとして、ファンに向き合えていない\nそんな人達に……負ける訳にはいかないって",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As idols‚ they aren't facing their fans.\nI can't lose… to people like that.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 377.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
