      "text": "……なんて言っても、結局緊張しちゃって\n全然眠れないでいるんですけどね……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Even though I say that‚ I ended up getting nervous and\nI can't sleep at all…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 385.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
